ic drawing</span><hr size=1> Ok, so im having problems with the whole comic drawing thing, i have a front cover and i have a script but i have a real problem with getting the right size boxes on the paper has anyone got any tips or anything that i could use? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=prismrx>PrismRX</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.freewebsitehosting.net/websites/OneWingedAngel/JG.txt" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(9/9/03 3:38 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2520.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.freewebsitehosting.net/websites/OneWingedAngel/JG.txt WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Manga comic drawing</span><hr size=1> Look at alot of them, mimic, customize. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#CCCCCC><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/bpolykarbonbbs.showUserPublicProfile?gid=dakarot@polykarbonbbs>Dakarot</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Fresh Meat</span><br> <font color=#336699>(9/11/03 7:35 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm4.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2520.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Manga comic drawing</span><hr size=1>    Yeah, i am having a little trouble too. Not so much with a boxes on the page, just things in general. I can draw normal anime pictures, I have started a few mangas, but I dont know, they're not like I want. Does anyone have any pointers, or tips that might help? Thanks.<br>
